    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "l1_text",
      "x": -64,
      "y": 83,
      "width": 465,
      "height": 85,
      "text": "Trigger: \"Request sent, no success\"\n         429  529  401  ECONNRESET\n\nResponse: Type-specific retry strategy\n         429 -> exponential backoff;  529 -> partition delay\n         401 -> OAuth refresh -> retry;  ECONNRESET -> immediate retry\n\nComponent: withRetry() AsyncGenerator",
      "originalText": "Trigger: \"Request sent, no success\"\n         429  529  401  ECONNRESET\n\nResponse: Type-specific retry strategy\n         429 -> exponential backoff;  529 -> partition delay\n         401 -> OAuth refresh -> retry;  ECONNRESET -> immediate retry\n\nComponent: withRetry() AsyncGenerator",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#FFFFFF",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
