      "y": 243,
      "width": 465,
      "height": 85,
      "text": "Trigger: \"Process gone, data persists\"\n         Ctrl+C  terminal close  crash\n\nResponse: JSONL chain rebuild from disk -> --resume continuation\n\nComponent: sessionStorage + conversationRecovery",
